            "description": "Real Stripe webhooks must be signed and the body must match the bytes Stripe sent (Postman re-encodes JSON, so signatures will not validate). Use the **Stripe CLI** (`stripe listen --forward-to localhost:8000/api/v1/orders/webhook/stripe`) for real testing.\n\n`metadata.type` ∈ `course` | `package` | `coursePackage`. `client_reference_id` = item id, `amount_total` in cents."
